), K&ouml;niggratz (1866) and Gravelotte (1870).<br/><br/>Lots of chrome rules, including command control,different weapon types and morale.  Nato style counters.  Four maps (3 large and 1 small). Inkerman,whilst fought on the smallest map due to the small battlefield, is a standout. Games are always close and are extremely accurate and well designed and researched. A well designed simulation.<br/><br/>",1993,,,
