s. They allow you to move around the board quickly. Moving from one cave entrance to another counts as one step.<br/><br/>You may move Blackbeard's ghost if you get a 6 on your dice-throw. Use him to help you and hinder other pirates. He may never leave the galleon. He may pass through a pirate in order to reach a square beyond him. He may enter a cabin occupied by a pirate.<br/><br/>You can fire the cannon, you can be made to &quot;walk the plank&quot; and can be saved from the water by a floating barrel.<br/><br/>",1991,,,
