ition  (1998)<br/>    Epic Armageddon - 4th Edition (2004)<br/>    NetEpic - unofficial continuation of 2nd Edition (1997)<br/>    Heresy - unofficial rules in same scale and setting, designed to be a grittier wargame.<br/><br/><br/>",1989,,,
