leonic Battles (OSG) - formerly known as the &quot;Napoleon's Last Battles (NLB-)Series&quot; <br/>- scale = 480m/hex, <br/>- time = 1hour/GT,<br/>- strength = 500-800 men/SP.<br/><br/><br/>Napoleon's Last Battles  was originally published by SPI then by TSR. The last 3rd edition was released by Decision Games.",1976,,,
