4513,Hand Drauf!,"['Memory', 'Open Drafting']","['Card Game', ""Children's Game"", 'Memory']","A simple card-based memory game. 21 cards showing two hand images in various colors are spread out on the table. On his turn, a player rolls a die and covers a hand image of the matching color. If he covers the last uncovered image on a card, he must announce the color of the other, previously covered, image. If he's correct, he gets the card as a point. If not, his turn ends and the next player takes his turn. Play continues until only 5 cards are left. Most cards won wins the game.<br/><br/>",2002,,,
