yched out?<br/><br/>Dr. Wayne Hardy: Veronica's husband and business partner.  He is attractive, friendly, and self-assured.  He and Veronica have it made.  Would he risk it all for revenge?<br/><br/>Wendy Larose: A high priced Madam.  She is quick-witted with loose morals.  Would she do anything, or anyone, to get what she wanted?<br/><br/>Randy Whalen: Police Officer for Lakeside's finest.  He was a forceful personality, not to be crossed.  Has crime and violence become a part of his nature?<br/><br/>",2002,,,
